data.description: Upon entering your condo, you are greeted by the breathtaking waterfront backdrop, immediately setting the tone for a tranquil and beautiful living experience. Adorned with high-quality finishes, including polished, stained concrete floors, upgraded cabinetry, and fixtures. The living room and master bedroom provide spacious areas with expansive views of the river, further enhancing the property's appeal. The unit offers the convenience of private storage (3rd Flr)  and parking (4th Flr #122), addressing practical needs and enhancing the overall living experience. 2 pets allowed 60lbs each. Secured building. New HVAC.
